Nigerian singer and songwriter, Adekunle Gold, popularly known as AG baby, took to Instagram in the early hours of Monday to celebrate his beloved wife, Simisola AKA Simi on her birthday. The music icon shared photos of his wife, declaring his undying love for Simi, Deja’s mum. “To the best part of my life, the thought of growing old with you makes me the happiest man. “My life is better because of you and I am grateful for every day, every milestone and moments with you. “Happy Birthday to the Most Beautiful Woman. I love you Magic. 💙,” he wrote. The duo got married in 2019 and welcomed their first child, a girl named Deja in 2020.